<br />\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。<br />\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。<br />\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。"},{"pid":"c96fc1c3d58940870cf2eedf227b2f0ff8e8c15c","tid":1407832,"uid":242708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpNm5ty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpNm5ty.png&h=4b4e5965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警犬正後退"},{"pid":"fcb85aeba70c61643ee690d7a581aa9debd872ab","tid":1407832,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedc97b1d3b3ea68da069e786442532adc0a872b","tid":1407832,"uid":242708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"281840f57e2f80c38088d0220870d454dcef59ad","tid":1407832,"uid":242708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33w3zoW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33w3zoW.png&h=992fb8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警犬縮左入左 未有動靜 其間有消防車經過"},{"pid":"75ef2ad64766ab4e2282090be044bca01b97f3af","tid":1407832,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14f5bee0ab8ee578bbdb6cb2d09bbaca5636349","tid":1407832,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75ef2ad64766ab4e2282090be044bca01b97f3af","tid":1407832,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"